  "response": "Trevor Noah is a South African comedian, television host, and author best known for his role as the host of \"The Daily Show,\" where he brought a unique perspective on current events and social issues, often drawing on his own experiences growing up in South Africa during apartheid. His humor often blends sharp wit with insights about race, politics, and culture, making his commentary both accessible and thought-provoking.\n\nIn addition to his work on television, Noah has received acclaim for his stand-up comedy and his autobiography, \"Born a Crime,\" which details his upbringing and highlights the complexities of identity and belonging. Overall, he is regarded as a significant voice in contemporary comedy and social commentary.",
